class:
class is an blueprint of an object.
before creating an object ,we need to define the class.
class contains all the related information.

Object:
Object is an instant of a class
It has any entity that has state and behaviour.
for ex. Bicycle is an object
It has state :gear
Behaviour:breaking,accelerating

