   2 parameteried(with or without returntype)
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   Method Overloading(compile time polymorphism):
   Same method name having different parameter
   
   Overload area()
   
   Constructor:
   -It is used to initialize data members
   -constructor name and class name is always same
   -It doesn't return any value
   -We call constructor at the time of object creation
   
   
   
